    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Cleved</placeName>
                <date>Apr 12 1861</date>
            </p>
            <p>Rev &amp; Dear Friend</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">I send you herewith<lb/> a brief history respecting the grand<lb/>
                metamorphose of the Tif<add>?</add> Israel Kabal<lb/> into a demi-semi-Gentile
                and<lb/> Jew church. Before coming to<lb/> preliminary trial of the
                    rejunction<add>?</add><lb/> last <date>Wednesday</date> the Trustees<lb/>
                stepped forward &amp; compromised<lb/> with me indemnifying me for my<lb/> loss of
                seats—I took by the advice<lb/> of my lawyer one of the best in<lb/> the State half
                of the original cost of<lb/> my seats &amp; have quitted the<lb/> Kabal forever. I
                shall shortly<lb/> unite myself with the old Congrega<lb/>-tion Anslie Chesed and
                trust to<lb/> accomplish something <hi rend="underline">there</hi>, worthy<lb/> the
                good cause. If you cannot insert<lb/> the enclosed article please send it<lb/> to
                the Jewish Messenger as I am determined<lb/> to have a public statement made of
                the<lb/> affair. I hope you will find room in your<lb/> valuable journal. More
                anon  In haste</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Yours truly  <persName role="author">B. F. Peixotto</persName></p>
        </body>
    </text>
